Database summary and statistics

This file contains a summary of the data currently available in the soil incubation database sidb. Currently, the number of entries in the database is 21. Most entries have multiple time-series of CO2 flux release from incubation experiments. The current total number of time-series is 290, and the total number of datapoints is 3312. The last entry was added on 2016-10-17.

Locations for which data are available are presented in the following map

A histogram of the incubation time for all entries can be obtained as

hist(incubationTime, xlab="Incubation time (days)", main ="", ylab="Number of studies")

Datasets

The file ~/scripts/plotEntry.R can be used to plot individual entries from the database. For example

source("~/sidb/scripts/plotEntry.R")
plotEntry(entry=Andrews2000SBB)
